@strongduanmu

Your config as follow doesn't work and actually use IdType.ID_WORKER to generate '1250240867332034561'  before executing sql.
```
@TableId(value = "code", type = IdType.NONE)
private String code;
```

In another word, you remove all sharding-jdbc config, it will be an error as the same.

A simple solution :
```
 @TableId(value = "code", type = IdType.UUID)
    private String code;
```

or

```
 @TableId(value = "code", type = IdType.AUTO)
    private String code;
```

